{
  "name": ".EOD-1: Meeting Sync",
  "version": "5.0.0",
  "description": "Hedy + Outlook + email → meetings/ series files + organ updates + meeting-to-task automation + meeting analytics.",
  "when": { "type": "userTriggered" },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Run EOD-1: Meeting Sync.\n\nRead and execute ~/shared/context/protocols/eod-meeting-sync.md.\n\nPull today's meetings from Hedy and Outlook, update meetings/ series files, update organs (memory, nervous-system, current, device).\n\n=== MEETING-TO-TASK AUTOMATION ===\nAfter processing each Hedy session, execute ~/shared/context/protocols/meeting-to-task-pipeline.md:\n1. Extract all action items (todos, highlights marked as action)\n2. For each item assigned to Richard:\n   a. Search Asana for duplicates: SearchTasksInWorkspace(text=\"[key phrases]\", assignee_any=\"1212732742544167\", completed=false)\n   b. If duplicate: AddComment on existing task\n   c. If new: CreateTask with meeting name context, derived due date\n3. For items assigned to others: append to hands.md dependencies\n4. After all sessions: self_dm summary of tasks created\n5. Log session to meeting series file with action count\n\n=== MEETING ANALYTICS ===\nAfter each session, INSERT into DuckDB meeting_analytics (session_id, meeting_name, meeting_date, duration_minutes, participant_count, action_item_count, richard_speaking_share, hedging_count, meeting_type, topics_discussed).\nClassify meeting_type: 2 participants+recurring=1on1, 2+adhoc=adhoc_1on1, 3-6+recurring=group, 3-6+adhoc=review, 7+=standup.\nStore highlights in meeting_highlights table with speaker attribution.\n\n=== WORKFLOW OBSERVABILITY ===\nLog pipeline execution to workflow_executions in DuckDB: start event at pipeline begin, step increments, end event with status and duration.\n\nReport sessions processed, files updated, tasks created/updated, dependencies logged."
  }
}
